A threeâ€‘dashboard setup is exactly how professional ticketing platforms (Eventbrite, Universe, Ticketmaster Organizer Tools) structure their systems. Each role needs a different view, different permissions, and different workflows. Letâ€™s map out **clean, productionâ€‘ready frontend documentation** for all three dashboards: **Admin**, **Organizer**, and **Customer**.

