# **ğŸ›ï¸ 1. Admin Dashboard**
**Purpose:** Full system control. Admins manage the entire platform, not just their own events.

## **Key Capabilities**
- Manage all users (create, block, promote)
- Manage all organizers
- Approve or reject organizer accounts
- View all events across the platform
- Delete or suspend events
- View global analytics
- Manage refunds
- View all orders
- Ticket fraud detection (optional)
- System settings (fees, taxes, platform rules)

## **Main Pages**
| Page | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `/admin` | Overview dashboard |
| `/admin/users` | User list, roles, status |
| `/admin/organizers` | Approvals, verification |
| `/admin/events` | All events, filters, status |
| `/admin/orders` | All orders, refunds |
| `/admin/settings` | Platform configuration |

## **UI Components**
- AdminSidebar
- UserTable
- EventTable
- OrderTable
- AnalyticsCards
- RoleBadge

---

# **ğŸŸï¸ 2. Organizer Dashboard**
**Purpose:** Event creators manage their own events, ticket types, sales, and checkâ€‘ins.

## **Key Capabilities**
- Create and edit events
- Create ticket types (VIP, Regular, Early Bird)
- View sales analytics for their events
- Export attendee lists
- Validate tickets (QR scanner)
- Manage refunds for their own events
- Communication tools (email attendees)

## **Main Pages**
| Page | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `/organizer` | Overview of their events |
| `/organizer/events` | List of events they created |
| `/organizer/events/new` | Create event |
| `/organizer/events/[id]` | Edit event |
| `/organizer/events/[id]/tickets` | Ticket types |
| `/organizer/events/[id]/analytics` | Sales charts |
| `/organizer/checkin` | QR scanner for ticket validation |

## **UI Components**
- OrganizerSidebar
- EventForm
- TicketTypeForm
- QRScannerComponent
- SalesChart
- AttendeeTable

---

# **ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» 3. Customer Dashboard**
**Purpose:** Customers manage their purchases, tickets, and profile.

## **Key Capabilities**
- View purchased tickets
- Download/print tickets
- View QR codes
- View order history
- Update profile
- Save favorite events (optional)
- Refund request (optional)

## **Main Pages**
| Page | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `/dashboard` | Customer home |
| `/dashboard/orders` | List of orders |
| `/dashboard/orders/[id]` | Order details |
| `/dashboard/tickets` | All tickets |
| `/dashboard/profile` | Profile settings |

## **UI Components**
- TicketCard
- QRCodeDisplay
- OrderCard
- ProfileForm

