# **ğŸ” Role-Based Access (Frontend)**

### **Admin**
```ts
role === "ADMIN"
```

### **Organizer**
```ts
role === "ORGANIZER"
```

### **Customer**
```ts
role === "CUSTOMER"
```

### **Route Protection Example**
```ts
export function requireRole(role: string) {
  const user = await apiGet("/auth/me");
  if (user.role !== role) redirect("/unauthorized");
  return user;
}
```

